Phases.Strategy: Coeurl O'Nine Tails are encountered twice in the instance. The second Coeurl also spawns two adds.

Mechanics.Name: Acid Mist
Mechanics.Description: Inflicts paralysis to all players hit.

Phases.Strategy: There are puddles of green goo surrounding the arena that inflict the Leaden debuff, slowing movement.

Mechanics.Name: Realm Shaker
Mechanics.Description: Instant circle AoE around the boss.

Mechanics.Name: Silkscreen
Mechanics.Description: A line AoE targeting a random player.

Mechanics.Name: Sticky Web
Mechanics.Description: Targets a random player, spawning an untargetable Fleshy Pod add at their position. The pod will then explode in a circle AoE inflicting any players hit with Poison.
